      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "樊素上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00002",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "学唱杨枝，习丝竹，喜咏歌词。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00003",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "咏絮看春柳，新歌踏竹枝。飘零无限恨，应有落花知。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00004",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "奴家，樊素。昔本上厅行首，今为白府侍儿。自幼善唱杨枝词，因此人人都唤奴作杨枝。昔蒙元微之、刘梦得两位名士，题诗所赠，遂得名播洛中，好不侥幸。这且不言。只因吾家太傅，这几日不知为了何事，常常烦闷，每日独宿花园。奴家也曾劝慰于他，奈仍然是长吁短叹。今日奴梳妆已毕，不免去到花园，慰问一番便了。",
      "text_length": 144
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00005",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "春三月艳阳天花飞片片，似这等斗芳菲紫姹红嫣。栏杆内芍药花朵朵争艳，有蝴蝶逐队儿上下蹁跹。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00006",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "来此花园，待我在此休息休息。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00007",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "樊素坐。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00008",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "咳，想我家太傅，致仕归家，名园居住。每日赋诗饮酒，品竹调丝，岂不悠游快乐。为何只是镇日愁烦，双眉不展。想我樊素，自入府以来，已有十年之久，蒙太傅十分眷爱，若不能猜破他的心事，与他除却愁烦，岂不辜负了他一番恩意？只是这个闷葫芦，叫我何处猜起呀！",
      "text_length": 121
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00009",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "有太傅每日里诗歌消遣，为什么愁眉皱这等忧烦。莫不是为良朋风流云散？莫不是为国家心内熬煎？莫不是为春残心中贪恋？莫不是为奴家减了红颜？闷奄奄转过了茶蘼小院，",
      "text_length": 77
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00010",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "见太傅却叫我怎样开言？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00011",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "樊素下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00012",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白居易上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00013",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "叹人生在世间如霜如电，有富贵和贫穷皆如是观。想当年好风流清肠缱绻，到如今鬓发白兴趣萧然。好一似那春蚕丝已将断，衰朽年病身躯能活几年！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00014",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "老夫白居易，表字乐天，太原人氏，唐室驾前为臣。初为翰苑词臣，历官太子太傅，沉浮宦海，四十余年。老夫今年已六十八岁，春蚕已老，蜡炬将灰。是吾致仕归里，虽然悠游自得，诗酒娱情倒也快乐。只奈近年，又患风痺之症，更觉老态龙钟。想吾的爱姬樊素，正在芳年，虽则两情眷爱，朝暮难离，倘若老夫一朝不测，岂不耽误了她的青春？仔细思量，倒不如开笼放鸟，使她另择佳偶，倒是一桩好事。还有裴令公，赠吾那一骑骆马，代步多年，留它何用。倒不如将它卖去，以省刍秣之资，岂不是好？正是：",
      "text_length": 227
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00015",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "落花有意随流水，流水无情恋落花。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00016",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子捧茶上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00017",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "请老爷用茶。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00018",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "院子。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00019",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00020",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "去至后堂，将素姬唤来见我。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00021",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
