      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "转来。再到厩中，将骆马牵来。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00023",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00024",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子转身望上场门。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00025",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "看素娘已分花拂柳而来。待我唤她一声。吓，素娘，老爷叫你到书房讲话。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00026",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "来了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00027",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "待吾到槽头牵马去者。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00028",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子下。樊素上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00029",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "听说是老太傅将奴呼唤，急忙间移莲步去问根源。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00030",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷万福。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00031",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。一旁坐下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00032",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "告坐。请问老爷，今日身体可好？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00033",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "咳！吾乃老病之身，还讲些什么好与不好？也不过是待死而已。吓素姬，你自入府以来，随侍老夫，有几年了？",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00034",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "将次十年了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00035",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "看老夫日来心烦意乱，你乃是聪明伶俐之人，可晓得老夫的心事？",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00036",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "奴见老爷这几日常常愁闷，正在狐疑。不知老爷，到底有何心事。妾身愚蠢，实难猜透。望老爷说个明白。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00037",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "咳，素姬呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00038",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "叹人生在世上如同梦幻，哪有这百年间不散的华筵。我有心放了你且回乡转，寻一个美满姻缘过上几年，嗳嗳嗳，过上几年。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00039",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷此话，从何说起？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00040",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "想老夫衰病残年，不能久于尘世。念你正在芳年，随同老夫，岂不耽误了你的终身。吾意欲放你归去，另配良缘，也不枉你跟随老夫一场。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00041",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷说哪里话来。想妾身自奉巾栉，并无过犯。仰蒙老爷，十分宠爱，正在无恩可报。况堂堂尚书之府，难道说就容不得妾身一人？嗳呀老爷呀，我樊素生是白府人，死是白府鬼。就是粉身碎骨，理所当然。若叫妾身另行改嫁，是断断不能从命的呀，吓吓！",
      "text_length": 113
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00042",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "樊素跪哭。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00043",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "素姬！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00044",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00045",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "嗳，樊素吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00046",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "劝爱姬休得要泪流满面，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00047",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "樊素！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00048",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00049",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "爱姬！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00050",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "主君！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00051",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "我那多情的素姬呀！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00052",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "回龙",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "叫一声多情姬细听我言：",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00053",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "非是我把恩情一旦割断，怕的是耽误你美貌芳年。没奈何只得做分飞之燕，出府去寻良匹另配良缘。有老夫黄泉路看堪不远，好一似沾泥絮莫再纠缠。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00054",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子牵马上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00055",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "纵出黄金价，难求千里驹。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00056",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "待我将马拴在栏杆之外。启老爷：骆马牵到。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00057",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "素姬，随老夫同去看来。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00058",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "妾身遵命。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00059",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "你看此马，赭流朱汗，竹耳霜蹄，锡鸾腾躣于康庄，房驷昭回于云汉。但是你口齿未老，吾的筋力已衰。世间自有阴阳，哪怕不得识主。今日老夫，致仕归田，无力养豢于你，要将你卖于他人，你好好另事新主去罢！",
      "text_length": 95
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00060",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马悲鸣连三。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00061",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "吓，老爷，你看着骆马蒙你乘骑多年，今日你要将它变卖，它竟不住悲鸣，深深恋主，不忍舍去之意。马尚如此，人岂无情？想我樊素，服侍老爷一场，蒙你十分眷爱，难道我反倒不如那牲畜么？事已至此，我实对老爷说了罢！老爷在一日，妾身便服侍你一日；老爷倘有不测，妾身一死，相从地下。耿耿此心，天日可鉴。咳，老爷呀！",
      "text_length": 148
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00062",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "胡琴多罗起顶板。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00063",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "说什么人在世如同梦幻，说什么耽误了美貌芳年。妾心愿纵然到海枯石烂，侍巾栉同衾枕永不变迁。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00064",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "吓，老爷，看这骆马同素娘，都是相依数载，同受恩养。今日恋恋，皆有不忍舍去之心。又听素娘一片言语，情词恳切，叫老奴也肝肠痛断，心似箭攒。望求老爷开恩，仍将素娘同骆马留下了罢！",
      "text_length": 86
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00065",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子哭。马鸣。樊素哭。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00066",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "呵！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00067",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "白乐天我本是慈心一片，怕的是辜负了良马、红颜。又谁知马悲鸣爱姬留恋，此时间反叫我意惹情牵。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00068",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "也罢，既然如此，也就罢了。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00069",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "骆马且莫嘶，素姬也免悲。汝等不我弃，彼此仍相依。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00070",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "家院，将马仍旧牵至后槽，要多加草料。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00071",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00072",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子牵马下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00073",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "想老夫只为此事，踌躇多日。不料今日，竟将满腹的愁烦，竟自到冰消雪化了。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00074",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷既然免却了愁烦，待妾身捧巵进酒，与老爷解闷。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00075",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "好。老夫生受你几杯。家院，看酒！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00076",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子捧酒，樊素接，斟三杯。笛吹柳叶锦牌。白居易连饮三杯。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00077",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "素姬，你把那杨柳枝词，与老夫歌上一曲。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00078",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "妾身遵命。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00079",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吹笛。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00080",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "一树春风万万枝，嫩于金色软于丝。永丰东角荒园里，尽日无人属阿谁。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00081",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白居易笑。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00082",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "清歌流丽如莺啭，不愧玉润与珠圆。满目愁云霎时散，打起精神且寻欢。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00083",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "自今以后，老夫倒愿……",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00084",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷你愿什么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00085",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "我与你——",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00086",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "在天愿作比翼鸟，在地愿为连理枝。天长地久有时尽，相爱相偎永不离。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00087",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "好一个相爱相偎永不离。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00088",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白居易、樊素同笑。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00089",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊素"
      ],
      "text": "老爷，今日园中芍药盛开，何不前去赏玩？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00090",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白居易"
      ],
      "text": "老夫正要前去赏玩。素姬，随老夫来呀。哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032008_e00091",
      "play_id": "01032008",
      "scene_id": "01032008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白居易、樊素同挽手下。",
      "text_length": 11
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}